{
  "page": "Lyonel Lorch",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lorch\" title=\"House Lorch\"><img alt=\"House Lorch.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/05/House_Lorch.png/50px-House_Lorch.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/05/House_Lorch.png/75px-House_Lorch.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/05/House_Lorch.png/100px-House_Lorch.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Lyonel Lorch</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant\" title=\"Faith Militant\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lorch\" title=\"House Lorch\">House Lorch</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant\" title=\"Faith Militant\">Faith Militant</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Lyonel Lorch</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lorch\" title=\"House Lorch\">House Lorch</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_Militant_uprising\" title=\"Faith Militant uprising\">Faith Militant uprising</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyonel_Lorch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the Faith Militant uprising, Ser Lyonel took up arms on behalf of the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Aenys_I)\" title=\"High Septon (Aenys I)\">High Septon</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Starry_Sept\" title=\"Starry Sept\">Starry Sept</a> against the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>. He fought in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_Great_Fork\" title=\"Battle at the Great Fork\">battle at the Great Fork</a> alongside Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rupert_Falwell\" title=\"Rupert Falwell\">Rupert Falwell</a> and other knights from the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>, as well as hundreds of <a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Poor Fellows</a>, against the royal army led by King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a> himself. It is unknown if he survived.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyonel_Lorch&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403131000\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.067 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.249 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 532/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10470/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5968/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 572/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 933/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtua